## Install / sync dependencies via uv
sync:
	uv sync

test:
    uv run pytest

## Lint with ruff
ruff:
	uv run ruff check src tests notebooks

## Format with ruff
format:
	uv run ruff format


## Static type checking (ty) - experimental alternative
ty:
	ty check src

## Run the standard quality checks
check: format ruff test

## Serve documentation locally
docs:
	uv run mkdocs serve
